@startuml
title AI Agent Gateway Sequence

participant Orchestrator
participant Gateway
participant Policy
participant Executor

Orchestrator -> Gateway: execution request + delegated identity
Gateway -> Policy: evaluate capability / scope / approval
Policy --> Gateway: allow / deny / conditions
alt allowed
  Gateway -> Executor: hand off execution
  Executor --> Gateway: response / callback registration
  Gateway --> Orchestrator: normalized response
else denied
  Gateway --> Orchestrator: rejection + reason
end
@enduml
